  variant: {
    default: "bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90",
    destructive: "bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground hover:bg-destructive/90",
    outline: "border border-input bg-background hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground",
    secondary: "bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80",
    ghost: "hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground",
    link: "text-primary underline-offset-4 hover:underline",
  },
  size: {
    default: "h-10 px-4 py-2",
    sm: "h-9 rounded-md px-3",
    lg: "h-11 rounded-md px-8",
    icon: "h-10 w-10",
  },
}
```

## Feature-Specific Components
- Place feature-specific components in `src/features/[feature]/components/`
- Use consistent naming patterns
- Export from `index.ts` for clean imports
- Follow the same styling patterns as base components

## Component Composition
- Use `asChild` prop for component composition
- Forward refs when needed
- Use Radix UI primitives for accessibility
- Implement proper ARIA attributes

## Loading States
- Use consistent loading patterns
- Implement skeleton loaders for better UX
- Handle loading states in feature components

